WEBVTT

00:00.999 --> 00:02.556
How far away is Mars?

00:03.479 --> 00:07.743
Well, it's 141 million miles from the sun, so, pretty far.

00:08.870 --> 00:09.943
Why is it red?

00:10.580 --> 00:12.784
Because its surface is made of iron oxide.

00:13.766 --> 00:15.535
Why do they call it Mars?

00:16.302 --> 00:19.363
Well, it was named after the Roman god of war.

00:21.069 --> 00:22.159
You're so smart, Dad.

00:25.349 --> 00:26.549
Did I ever tell you about Jupiter?

